The Team shall consist of the following 18 individuals appointed by the Department:
12 members including:
1 holder of a tidal fisheries license;
1 crab processor;
1 oyster packer;
1 surf clam processor;
1 finfish processor;
1 value-added processor;
1 wholesale distributor;
1 seafood distributor;
1 aquafarmer;
1 representative of the Chesapeake Bay Seafood Industries Association;
1 representative of the Maryland Watermen's Association; and
1 representative of the Seafood Marketing Advisory Commission; and
6 advisors, including 1 representative each from:
The University of Maryland, College Park;
The University of Maryland Eastern Shore;
The Department;
The Department of the Environment;
The Department of Natural Resources; and
The Department of Health and Mental Hygiene.
